c: 16
v: 71
t: "Kandi Allah yarutishije bamwe muri mwe abandi mu butunzi. Nyamara babandi barutishijwe abandi, ntibashobora kwemera guha imitungo yabo abacakara babo kugira ngo bareshye mu butunzi. (Ese niba mutemera kureshya n’abagaragu banyu, ni gute mureshyeshya Imana n’ibigirwamana?) Nonese bahakana ingabire za Allah"